OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start to the
OL,6,Fday with a few light showers about,
OL,7,Fchiefly across southern districts, but
OL,8,Fthese should die away by late morning
OL,9,Fwith brighter spells building into the
OL,10,Fdry afternoon. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry night with late
OL,13,Fsunshine then clear spells, though
OL,14,Fhigher cloud increasing overnight.
OL,15,FWinds increasing to a fresh
OL,16,Fsoutheasterly across the coasts
OL,17,Ftowards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
