OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA dry morning with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine. Cloud increasing during the
OL,7,Fafternoon to bring some patchy light
OL,8,Frain from late evening. East to
OL,9,Fsoutheast breezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FUnsettled with a series of rain bands
OL,13,Fcrossing from the west. However, with
OL,14,Fwinds staying southwesterly
OL,15,Ftemperatures a little up on the
OL,16,Fseasonal averages.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
